'''Noloh Gunga Bongoform''' was a vehicle manufacturing company based in [[Noloh Gunga Fuel Station]], in [[The Three Jetties]] District of [[Bartyn's Landing]], a town in [[Lamaredd/Legends|Lamaredd]]. Contrarily to most business there, the factory did not belong to the [[Bartyn family]].

